:null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a59c/6b8b/443436_mini.png?m=1653542864","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a59c/6b8b/443436_normal.png?m=1653542864","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a59c/6b8b/443436_large.png?m=1653542864","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a59c/6b8b/443436_xlarge.png?m=1653542864","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a59c/6b8b/443436_xlarge.png?m=1653542864","created":1569484891,"last_modified":1653542864},"last_reply_by":"hldevelop369","last_touched":1659430586,"title":"关于一个私活报价的问题","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/870239","created":1659426485,"deleted":0,"content":"大概功能在这给了个简易的图\r\nhttps://imgur.com/a/V5SJQPa\r\n他写的也比较抽象\r\n就是 OA 审批\r\nABC 三个角色.\r\nC 先定义一些表格 Excel 什么的.\r\nA 提交内容(表格,图片,文字)给 B 审核,B 同意后再提交给 C.....\r\n中间可能还会涉及到一些界面.\r\n1.注册登录模块.(小程序应该是直接关联微信号,这里可以省略)\r\n2.权限等级设置.(感觉也可以过滤掉,我后台直接指定.节约成本)\r\n3.C 角色设置表单样式.界面\r\n4.A 角色提交界面.(表单详情)\r\n5.与用户相关的表单列表界面(提交和处理的处理记录).\r\n6.本单位人员列表.\r\n7.个人资料界面\r\n\r\n大概就分析出了这么几个界面.\r\n\r\n\r\n我本身 android 开发的,后台也会一些这个需求比较简单.\r\n没弄过小程序.不知道小程序多少合适.\r\n感觉还能给我时间学.\r\n\r\n\r\n很多东西都不明确也没有界面.说是对界面没有需求,只要功能出来就行.\r\n对接端是 ZF..不知道有没有坑.","content_rendered":"大概功能在这给了个简易的图<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://imgur.com/a/V5SJQPa\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://imgur.com/a/V5SJQPa</a><br />他写的也比较抽象<br />就是 OA 审批<br />ABC 三个角色.<br />C 先定义一些表格 Excel 什么的.<br />A 提交内容(表格,图片,文字)给 B 审核,B 同意后再提交给 C.....<br />中间可能还会涉及到一些界面.<br />1.注册登录模块.(小程序应该是直接关联微信号,这里可以省略)<br />2.权限等级设置.(感觉也可以过滤掉,我后台直接指定.节约成本)<br />3.C 角色设置表单样式.界面<br />4.A 角色提交界面.(表单详情)<br />5.与用户相关的表单列表界面(提交和处理的处理记录).<br />6.本单位人员列表.<br />7.个人资料界面<br /><br />大概就分析出了这么几个界面.<br /><br /><br />我本身 android 开发的,后台也会一些这个需求比较简单.<br />没弄过小程序.不知道小程序多少合适.<br />感觉还能给我时间学.<br /><br /><br />很多东西都不明确也没有界面.说是对界面没有需求,只要功能出来就行.<br />对接端是 ZF..不知道有没有坑.","last_modified":1659426504,"replies":24,"id":870239},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_large.png?m=1595507885","name":"ideas","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_normal.png?m=1595507885","title":"奇思妙想","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ideas","topics":5090,"footer":"","header":"让你的创意在这里自由流动吧。","title_alternative":"Ideas","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_mini.png?m=1595507885","stars":2634,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":519,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":382312,"username":"ggp1ot2","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ggp1ot2","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da2c/7a71/382312_mini.png?m=1655554833","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da2c/7a71/382312_normal.png?m=1655554833","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da2c/7a71/382312_large.png?m=1655554833","created":1549503424,"last_modified":1655554833},"last_reply_by":"xygod","last_touched":1659431856,"title":"求推荐一款好用的待办事项软件。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/870225","created":1659423902,"deleted":0,"content":"最近一直在找一个待办事项 /待办任务 /提醒类型的软件。\r\n\r\n当然在这个领域的软件这么成熟的时代，我还是找不到一个让我用的舒服的。\r\n\r\n在之前，我曾用过很久的滴答清单 /印象笔记，但最终都放弃了。\r\n\r\n添加一个事项要设置很多无用的分组、类型、提醒等。\r\n\r\n软件功能越做越复杂，总要浪费时间在无用的点击上。\r\n\r\n最近在用 notion 和苹果自带的待办事项，但总感觉用起来不丝滑。\r\n\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n吐槽完毕，我的需求很简单，就是单纯的待办事项记录。\r\n\r\n更有点像便利贴，就是有一堵墙，我想起来什么事情，我就写一个便利贴贴上去，搞定了我就揭下来。\r\n\r\n我一眼看过去，就知道我有哪些事情要做，因为都是我贴的，我也记得哪个区域的事情紧急度高一点。\r\n\r\n不需要 APP 有很多复杂的功能，什么文件夹啊，分类啊，主题啊，提醒啊等等。\r\n\r\n不用的时候就老老实实的呆在手机里，不要各种推送。\r\n\r\n点开就能一目了然的看到我还有哪些事儿，添加一个新事件，点一下就能写。\r\n\r\n如果可以，最好可以多设备同步（我需要常在 macos 、windows 、ios 之间切换）。","content_rendered":"<p>最近一直在找一个待办事项 /待办任务 /提醒类型的软件。</p>\n<p>当然在这个领域的软件这么成熟的时代，我还是找不到一个让我用的舒服的。</p>\n<p>在之前，我曾用过很久的滴答清单 /印象笔记，但最终都放弃了。</p>\n<p>添加一个事项要设置很多无用的分组、类型、提醒等。</p>\n<p>软件功能越做越复杂，总要浪费时间在无用的点击上。</p>\n<p>最近在用 notion 和苹果自带的待办事项，但总感觉用起来不丝滑。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>吐槽完毕，我的需求很简单，就是单纯的待办事项记录。</p>\n<p>更有点像便利贴，就是有一堵墙，我想起来什么事情，我就写一个便利贴贴上去，搞定了我就揭下来。</p>\n<p>我一眼看过去，就知道我有哪些事情要做，因为都是我贴的，我也记得哪个区域的事情紧急度高一点。</p>\n<p>不需要 APP 有很多复杂的功能，什么文件夹啊，分类啊，主题啊，提醒啊等等。</p>\n<p>不用的时候就老老实实的呆在手机里，不要各种推送。</p>\n<p>点开就能一目了然的看到我还有哪些事儿，添加一个新事件，点一下就能写。</p>\n<p>如果可以，最好可以多设备同步（我需要常在 macos 、windows 、ios 之间切换）。</p>\n","last_modified":1659423967,"replies":22,"id":870225},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":188122,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3523,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":477915,"username":"dtgxx","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dtgxx","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0d477d0a6d67ec2d7eeb09a3fe544a5a?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0d477d0a6d67ec2d7eeb09a3fe544a5a?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0d477d0a6d67ec2d7eeb09a3fe544a5a?s=73&d=retro","created":1584723179,"last_modified":1641019944},"last_reply_by":"akakidz","last_touched":1659422203,"title":"v 吧的大佬们， 34 层顶楼是不是会漏水啊","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/870171","created":1659412092,"deleted":0,"content":"我买了 12 楼，正在准备装修，还有个 34 楼，朋友想买，但是不知道顶楼是不是一定会漏水啊。顶楼比次顶楼便宜 20w 呢。。。v 吧大佬们给建议建议。","content_rendered":"我买了 12 楼，正在准备装修，还有个 34 楼，朋友想买，但是不知道顶楼是不是一定会漏水啊。顶楼比次顶楼便宜 20w 呢。。。v 吧大佬们给建议建议。","last_modified":1659412092,"replies":22,"id":870171},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1659331259","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1659331259","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":50094,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1659331259","stars":7918,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":281444,"username":"Oktfolio","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Oktfolio","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f23f/09d0/281444_mini.png?m=1649742190","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f23f/09d0/281444_normal.png?m=1649742190","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f23f/09d0/281444_large.png?m=1649742190","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f23f/09d0/281444_xlarge.png?m=1649742190","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f23f/09d0/281444_xlarge.png?m=1649742190","created":1515575007,"last_modified":1649742190},"last_reply_by":"wangtian2020","last_touched":1659428964,"title":"开发团队菜得一批，是不是该提桶跑路啊？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/870206","created":1659421247,"deleted":0,"content":"我司存在 XSS 、CSRF 、SQL 注入、固定 SESSIONID 漏洞\r\n\r\n一个几千万用户的平台，「该有」的漏洞全都有......\r\n\r\n虽然设置了 httponly ，脚本拿不到 cookie ，但是脚本确实能执行......\r\n\r\n\r\n屎山都已经没法形容那些代码了......\r\n\r\n上百万的代码（不少是 MBG 生成的），只有 100 多个 toString()，还基本都是我写的......\r\n\r\n\r\n是不是该提桶跑路啊......","content_rendered":"<p>我司存在 XSS 、CSRF 、SQL 注入、固定 SESSIONID 漏洞</p>\n<p>一个几千万用户的平台，「该有」的漏洞全都有......</p>\n<p>虽然设置了 httponly ，脚本拿不到 cookie ，但是脚本确实能执行......</p>\n<p>屎山都已经没法形容那些代码了......</p>\n<p>上百万的代码（不少是 MBG 生成的），只有 100 多个 toString()，还基本都是我写的......</p>\n<p>是不是该提桶跑路啊......</p>\n","last_modified":1659421247,"replies":19,"id":870206},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1635654723","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1635654723","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":11157,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723","stars":571